{"tid":2078282,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 拉登現身觀眾席, 觀看英冠比賽","createTime":"2020-06-25T02:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T04:01:21.000Z","uid":34571,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c362f2f63b862143a2e4637cf89daebd927a553f","tid":2078282,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/06/25/5/5c41cd56088a92a4d3029b9e0af2adea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F06%2F25%2F5%2F5c41cd56088a92a4d3029b9e0af2adea.jpg&h=364e8fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在英冠列斯聯隊的看台上，竟然出現了本拉登的形象，球會不得不採取相應措施。<br />\n<br />\n  因為疫情導致空場比賽，球會為了給球場增添氣氛，設置了球迷照片板的環節，球迷們可以出錢將自己的形象展現在看台上。但有人發現，「本拉登」也來看球了。一名球迷在網絡平台上說：「天哪，我旁邊是本拉登！」另一人也發現不對：「他們把我放在了本拉登身邊！」還有人評論說：「我無法理解，這一幕是怎麼鬧出來的，全程就沒有人注意到嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n  對此，列斯聯球會的一位發言人表示，本拉登的照片已經被去除，球會將進行嚴格檢查，確保再沒有任何有爭議的照片出現在看台上。"},{"pid":"23bfa32f70a0279d9fe4de84b324bb9f04890d66","tid":2078282,"uid":56744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T03:06:18.000Z","msg":"BLM!!!!"},{"pid":"8f658a33984105353c9f9f0bc7e05507e0c58fc7","tid":2078282,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T03:09:35.000Z","msg":"Semitics lives matter<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e433401b05132f057f55318c71367085cbd4ace4","tid":2078282,"uid":3080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYGqt84.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYGqt84.png&h=8eff2162&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5eaa3d93ac5953b150bfa5d735f113de58328cfd","tid":2078282,"uid":241296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/